{
  "texts": [
    "In this proof, we need additional notation.",
    "Let V cyc,0 denote the set of cycle nodes having the same community as v 1 and v 2.",
    "For k = 1,.",
    ", I let V cyc,k be the set of cycle nodes of community k. For short, we write V cyc,̸ =0 = ∪ I k=1 V cyc,k.",
    "We consider separately cycle edges and fastener edges."
  ]
}